title: Amba Mangalam
lyrics:
1. Amba mangalam jagadamba mangalam 
Mangalaa roopuni gauri mangalam
2.vani mangalam kalyani mangalam
Omkara swarupini Devi mangalam
3.Amba mangalam bramaraamba mangalam
Parama shivuni hrdhyarani gauri mangalam
4.janani mangalam jagajanani mangalam
Mulloka sancharini Amma managalam
5.shakthi mangalam shiva shakthi mangalam
Ardhanareeshwari gauri mangalam
6. Lalitha mangalam shubha charitha mangalam
Sri tripura sundari Devi mangalam
(Amba mangalam………)

title: Gopala
lyrics:
Gopala Radha Lola murali Lola nandalala (2)
Keshava Madhava janardhana (2)
Vanamala brindaavana baala (2)
Murali Lola nanndalala(2)
Gopala Radha Lola
Murali Lola nandalala
Murali Lola nandalala
Hare nandalala
Hare nandala

title: Hara Om
lyrics: Hara om hara om sadha shiva Hari om hari om narayana(2) Pannaga bhooshana Sadha shiva Pannaga shayana narayana Kailash Vaasa sadhshiva  Vaikunta Vaasa narayana (hara)  Gowri sametha sadhashiva Lakshmi sametha narayana  Shambho mahadeva sadhashiva Ambuja nayana narayana (hara)  Padma vibhushitha sadhashiva  Srigandha lebitha narayana Andha rakshka sadhashiva  Aabath baandhava narayana  Hara…………narayana(2)

title: Hey Murali Madhava
lyrics: Hey murali madhava radhe krishna keshava  Keshava madhava yadhava nandana  Radhe krishna Jeya Gopal (2) 1.nanda nandana radhe shyam  Indhu vadana megha shyam (2) keshava…. 2. Baktha vatsala radhe shyam Bhaagavathapriya megha shyam(2) keshava…. 3. Kaaliya nandana radhe shyam  Kamsa nishooshadana megha shyam (2) keshava… 4.paandu ranga radhe shyam  Pandari natha megha shyam(2) keshava… Hey murali madhava radhe krishna keshava Radhe krishna Jeya Gopal  Radhe krishna Jeya Gopal

title: Rama Nama Tharakam
lyrics: Rama Rama Rama Rama Rama Nama thaarakam  Rama Krishna vasudeva bhakthi mukthi dayakam}2 Janaki manoharam sarva Loka nayakam (2) Shankaradhi sevyamana punya nama keerthanam (2) Rama………dayakam  Veera shoora vandhitham raavanaadhi naashakam (2) Aanjaneya jeeva nama raaja mantra roopakam (2) Rama…………dayakam  Rama krishna Vasudeva bhakthi mukthi dayakam(2)

title: Rama Raghava
lyrics: Rama ragahava Jeya Seetha naayaka (2) Rama raghava raajeeva lochana  Kamitha phaladha karivaradha (2)  Krishna keshava jeya gopi vallabha (2) Krishna yeshiva ambuja lochana  Vaanchitha phaladha yadhuvaradha (2) Rama ragahava jeya seetha nayaka Jeya seetha nayaka Jeya seetha nayaka

title: Shivaya
lyrics: Shivaya nama om shivaya namaha  Shivaya nama om nama Shivaya (2) Shivaya nama om Shivaya namha  Shivaya nama om nama shivaya(2) 1.	Shiva shiva shiva Shivaya nama om Hara hara hara Narayana nama om(2) Shivaya nama om Shivaya namaha  Shivaya nama om nama Shivaya  2.	Shiva shiva shanmukha guhaya nama om Hara hara hara sharavana bhavaya nama om(2) Shivaya nama om Shivaya namaha  Shivaya nama om nama Shivaya(2) Nama Shivaya nama Shivaya

title: Varuvai
lyrics: Varuvai varuvai varuvai amma(2) Thiruve uruvai varuvai amma(2) Irulai neekida varuvai amma(2) Undhan arulai  pozindhidu thaaye Amma(2) Varuvai varuvai varuvai Amma  Thiruve uruvai varuvai Amma  Kalyani karumaari kamakshi neeye (2) Mahalakshmi mathangi meenakshi neeye(2) Varalakshmi vaaraahi Visalakshi neeye(2) Ulagaalum maaye Prashanthi thaaye (2) Varuvai ………
